quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  18,16,"Tuma nde danndi on gaayi yim…ìe mon …ìen, terti…óon ko …ìe rewata kon gaanin Alla, on rewaali si wanaa Alla Kanko tun, fattoyagol ngol ka fammeere fii dogidugol e diina mon kan Joomi mon Senii…óo On hiMo weftana=wertana on immorde e Yurmeende Makko nden ko hiMo reenira on …óun immorde e ay…ìe mon O hiwa on kadi, O niwinana on e fiyaake mon ko hi…óon nafitora …óun, konko lontinanta on e ngurdan…óan hakkunde yim…ìe mon."
  18,17,"∆Åe ja…ìi ko …ìe yamiraa kon, Alla li…ìi …óoyngol e ma…ì…ìe, O reeni …ìe e ga√±o ma…ì…ìe on. A yi'ay -an sutii…óo …ìe- naange ngen si nge ∆¥ellitike ka fu…óirde magge hinge oo√±ora e fammeere ma…ì…ìe nden ka senngo √±aamo naatungo ngon e mayre, si nge wirnike ka mutugol magge nge selirana nde ka senngo nano mayre nge hewtataa nde, kam…ìe hi…ìe e …óowde duumiindi nguli naange ngen tampintaa …ìe, kam…ìe hi…ìe e yaajeende ka fammeere henndu ndu …ìe hatonnjini ndun e mu'un no hewtude …ìe, …óun ko …ìe he…ìi immorde e wernugol …ìe ka fammeere, e li…ìugol …óoyngol e ma…ì…ìe, e oo√±agol naange ngen e ma…ì…ìe, e yaajugol nokkuure ma…ì…ìe nden, e danndugol …ìe bone yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen: Ko jeyaa…óun e kaaweeji Golle Alla tinndin…óe e Katta…óe Makko, kala mo Alla hawrinndini e Laawol Peewal ko on woni feewu…óo e goonga, on Mo o tertii…óun e gaayi maggol O majjini mo, a he…ìantaa mo walloowo mo no hawrinndina mo e Peewal, o fewna mo e maggal; sabu fewnugol ngol ko e Junngo Alla woni, wonaa e juu…óe makko kanko."
  18,18,"A sikkay …ìe -an ndaaroowo …ìe- ko …ìe finu…ìe sabu udditagol gite ma…ì…ìe, ko selli kon kam…ìe ko …ìe …óaanii…ìe, Me…óen waylitira …ìe e nder …óoyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol tumagoo √±aamo, tumagoo kadi nano, fii wata leydi ndin √±aamu …ìalli ma…ì…ìe …óin, rawaandu ma…ì…ìe setodundu ndun e ma…ì…ìe hindu focci koy…óe mayru ka damal fammeere nden, sinno a yaltitiino e ma…ì…ìe yi'u…óaa …ìe a huccitayno e ma…ì…ìe dogaa sabu hulugol …ìe, wonkii maa heewayno kulol ma…ì…ìe."
  18,19,"Ko wano Men wa…óirani …ìe nii, ko Men jantii kon immorde e hawnii…ói Kattan…óe Amen, Men finndini …ìe …ìaawo dummunne juutu…óo fii yo wo…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe lanndo wo…ì…ìe fii on dummunne mo …ìe …ìooyi …óaanaade e mun, wo…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe jaabii: "En √±ii…ìii e nder …óoygol √±allal maa…óun yoga e √±allal." Wo…ì…ìe e ma…ì…ìe jaabii, o mo fee√±anaali …óun dummunne √±ii…ìugol ma…ì…ìe e …óoyngol: "Ko Joomi mon woni Anndu…óo dummunne √±ii…ìugol mon ko on …óaanii…ìe, …ìe fawee e Makko ganndal …óun jokkee ko ndaari on kon, nulee go…ó…óo e mon wonndude e …óii mbuu…ói mon kaalise …óoo ka saare me'en woowaande, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e yim…ìe mayre …ìuri laa…ìude √±aametee …ìuri laa…ìude kadi wonirde, yo o molto ka naatugol saare nden e ka yaltugol nde e ka huuwondiral makko, yo o wonu ∆¥o∆¥u…óo, wata o accu gooto annda fii nokkuure mon nden; sabu ko …óun addata kon immorde e lorra maw…óo.""
  18,20,"Pellet, yim…ìe mon …ìen si …ìe yaltitii e mon …ìe anndii nokku mon, …ìe wariray on fi…óirgol on kaa∆¥e, maa…óun …ìe artira on e laawol ma…ì…ìe …ìoyliingol ngol, ngol ngol wonuno…óon e mu'un ko adii Alla Neeminirde on Peewal faade e Goonga kan, si on artii e maggol on maletaake poomaa, wanaa ka ngurndan aduna wanaa ka laahara kadi, ko woni, on hayray e aduna e laahara hayrere mawnde nden sabu …óalugol moo…óon Diina Goonga ha kan, kan ka Alla Fewni on e mun, artugol moo…óun e ngol laawol …ìuyleengol."